room_title: Escape room "The Red Room Murder" by Southernmost Escape in Key West
room_address: 2782 N Roosevelt Blvd. Key West, FL 33040
room_description: You are a Private Investigator that has been hired by a rich trust fund playboy. The playboy has found a  woman murdered in his infamous “Red Room” and there is no shortage of suspects. Do you have what it takes to find the murderer in 60 minutes or less before the authorities arrive and arrest your client?
